---++ Local Condor setup

As with all the other hands-on exercises, we will be using &lt;br&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;vdt-itb.cs.wisc.edu&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br&gt;
to submit and monitor our jobs.

The glidein factory using &lt;b&gt;yet another Condor installation&lt;/b&gt;.
In order to see it, please run (in a clean terminal session):
&lt;pre&gt;
[sfiligoi@vdt-itb ~]$ source  /home/gfactory/glidecondor/condor.sh
&lt;/pre&gt;

At any given point, you can check you are using the right one by using:
&lt;pre&gt;
[sfiligoi@vdt-itb ~]$ which condor_q
/home/gfactory/glidecondor/bin/condor_q
[sfiligoi@vdt-itb ~]$ echo $CONDOR_CONFIG
/home/gfactory/glidecondor/etc/condor_config
[sfiligoi@vdt-itb ~]$ 
&lt;/pre&gt;

